Features
Features: CORSAIR AirGuide Technology: Utilizes anti-vortex vanes to channel concentrated airflow and improve cooling, whether used as intake, exhaust, or mounted to a liquid cooling radiator or heatsink.

Magnetic Levitation Bearing: Dramatically reduces friction, producing lower noise, higher performance, and longer-lasting durability.

Keep Your System Cool: Powerful PWM-controlled fan speeds from 450 RPM up to 2,000 RPM with zero RPM mode support, pushing up to 58.1 CFM of air with 2.9mm-H2O of static pressure.

Eight Vibrant Red LEDs: Create brilliant lighting with eight LEDs along each fan hub.

Low Noise, High Performance: A translucent 120mm fan blade spins quietly even at full speed, providing high airflow while letting your LED lighting shine through.
